{"title":"(13) implementacion-amb-sysmayal2 - Raven","url":"https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-implementacion-amb-sysmayal2","summary":"This is a project implementation tracking page for AMB-Wellness through the Raven messaging system. The page documents the progress of a multi-phase implementation project. Phase 1 was successfully completed, followed by Phase 2 which focused on optimization and was marked as complete with 13 files pushed to GitHub. Phase 2 involved splitting large files into smaller modules including workflows.py (62KB split into 6 modules) and agent.py (70KB split into 5 modules). Currently, Phase 3 is in progress, focusing on implementing a quality management system with 5 detailed subtasks spanning 20 days, including quality document configuration, non-conformity system, internal audits, management indicators, and training. Phase 4 (Scale) is planned for future implementation involving microservices migration and multi-region support.","key_points":["Phase 1 Task Assignment was completed successfully","Phase 2 Optimization is complete with 13 files pushed to GitHub repository (rogerboy38/raven_ai_agent)","Phase 2 involved splitting workflows.py (62KB) into 6 modules: cache_layer.py, queue_handlers.py, smart_delivery.py, smart_invoice.py, bom_helpers.py, tds_resolver.py","Phase 2 involved splitting agent.py (70KB) into 5 modules: agent_prompts.py, memory_manager.py, context_builder.py, command_router.py, agent.py","Performance test suite (perf_test.py) created with 270 lines","Phase 3 focuses on Quality Management System implementation with 5 subtasks over 20 days","Phase 3 subtask 1: Quality Document Configuration (Days 1-3)","Phase 3 subtask 2: Non-Conformity System (Days 4-7)","Phase 3 subtask 3: Internal Audits (Days 8-12)","Phase 3 subtask 4: Management Indicators (Days 13-16)","Phase 3 subtask 5: Training and Competencies (Days 17-20)","Phase 4 planned: Microservices migration, auto-scaling rules, multi-region support, advanced analytics","Team includes Administrator Technical Support, Alvaro Ceniceros, Daniel Flores, Ernesto Beltran, Alan, and Alicia Medina","Deploy commands provided for pulling updates and restarting Docker containers","Zero breaking changes maintained in Phase 2 refactoring"],"relevant_links":["https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-implementacion-amb-sysmayal2","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/threads","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/saved-messages","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-marketing","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-manufacturing","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-batch-lote102","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-amb-general","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-shipping","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-quality-inspector","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-quality","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-maintenance-amb-w"],"file_name":"amb_wellness_implementation_phase3.json"}
